aces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T09:35:49.000Z","msg":"識人係咁，仲要第二年先報pgde"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T11:05:47.000Z","msg":"唔係fd底邊有校長會揀"},{"pid":"fc647c8d575a7e770ba9df5d0acee2ec4e7d291e","tid":913730,"uid":160579,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T02:45:44.000Z","msg":"教大就算鳩數啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> hku cu bu甚至lu都大把選擇<br />\n洗鬼要你咩"},{"pid":"2b9c9716c2546a8e571938cc25e0201a26601f99","tid":913730,"uid":34793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T02:56:22.000Z","msg":"教院就教院啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  i大就話姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8363df18c54df92d066dc346c8d0c48576251b2a","tid":913730,"uid":170438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T02:58:51.000Z","msg":"讀 master"},{"pid":"b2c527f020b175d8421fca4661572a48a344b4c1","tid":913730,"uid":14956,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T03:36:12.000Z","msg":"屌都唔明做乜鳩 人地問下啫 樓主又冇引戰又冇講嘢1999 屌人地問下啫 大部分人係度串鳩樓主做乜嘢事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺得其實睇你點present你自己 因為你冇小學教學經驗 你都知個模式唔同㗎啦 你試下啲唔係一二線、冇咁好嘅小學應該有機 或者claim自己係耶撚然後去天主基督教學校都有機 <br />\n利申：識人做咗5年補習社入返一間係炮台山小學用英文教數學 佢教大數2nd up畢業 英文4"},{"pid":"ab1a99a039a16f7d0f206d480ae3362daf1d840d","tid":913730,"uid":199420,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"c3555a6e8fc824dc27aebf2b53fff847fcb04893","tid":913730,"uid":199420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T15:35:07.000Z","msg":"教大中文系畢業<br />\n教左補習社一年半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無讀pdge<br />\n想轉入小學教中文<br />\n機會大嗎？？<br />\n有無教緊書既爸絲打比d意見？？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T11:28:37.000Z","msg":"報告<br />\n已經喺新界區一間小學搵到工，普通小學，非名校<br />\n職位支援老師，人工0.7CM，要入班教書<br />\n已經打算補讀番教育文憑，希望讀完做番1CM<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然我面試頭兩間小學都失敗了，但到左第三間小學，校長就睇中我可以幫手教埋課後留校學生的功課輔導班，就決定請左我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 出社會最緊要睇清楚職業生涯條路如何規劃，用恆心＋毅力一步一腳印，堅持到既人先會成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nAnyway，我已經睇清楚自己條路點行，唔理連登既巴絲打留言用咩語氣黎提醒我，我會視為前進既動力<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e87c1f2609d49438781e41f739f178eb8963fda","tid":913730,"uid":174159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T11:33:09.000Z","msg":"我日日都諗住辭職，做乜咁傻自己走入學校"}]}